help:
**List of all commands:**
 * means not working
 [] are required parameters {} are optional
 !ping | Just responds with pong, an essential command for all discord bots
 !setgame [game] | Sets what it's playing
 !vote [something] | Sets your "vote" to whatever you say
 !getvotes | Lists everyone vote
 !repeat [text] | Repeats something
 !bothappy | Gets if the bot is happy or not
 good bot | Adds to bots happiness by one
 bad bot | Subtracts the bots happiness by one
 !explosion or !megumin | Sends a bomb
 * !roulette | Has a 1/6 chance to multiply your money or get rid of it all
 !balance | Says how much money you have
 * !blackjack | Lets you play a game of blackjack
 * !5draw | Lets you play some 5 draw poker
 !roll {die} | Rolls a die. By default the die is a d6 but you can choose custom ones written in the format {rolls}D[sides]
 !flip | Flips a coin
 !tell [name] [text] | Just tells someone something
 !newvote [vote] | Clears all votes and announces in the chat a new vote for something
 * !play | Play a song
 !id | Says some information about the bot
 !buy | Buys an item
 !inv | Shows what you have in your inventory
 !use | Uses an item in your inventory
 * !subupdates | Sends bot updates to the channel the command is ran in
 !wint | Sends an invite to the Wint discord server, where you can get help with the bot
 !help | Sends this list of commands
 !invite | Generates a link to add the bot to your server
 !dungeon | Creates a dungeon using donjons dungeon generator
 !dungeoncredit | Says who made the dungeon generator (donjon)
!imbored | Gives you a random site to waste five seconds on

 **List of items:**
 Lenny - Lets you easily put a lenny face in the chat
 Cheese - Gives a 2x earnings multiplier for 10 minutes
 Coffee
 Gun
